50|$|The International Wool Textile Organisation (IWTO) is the {{international}} body representing {{the interests of the}} world's wool-textile trade and industry. IWTO membership covers woolgrowers, traders, primary processors, spinners, weavers, garment makers and retailers of wool and <b>allied</b> <b>fibres</b> in its member-countries, as well as all kind of organizations related to wool products and the wool business in general.|$|E
